    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AnalyticsCounter
    The AnalyticsCounter class analyses symptom data.
    ISymptomReader
    Reads symptom data from a source and returns a list of strings, possibly with duplicates and unordered, or an empty list if no data is available.
    ISymptomWriter
    Writes symptom data to a file, with each symptom on a new line, accepts a list of strings representing the symptoms, and has a method to retrieve symptom data from the file, returning a list of strings.
    Main
    The main class to run the AnalyticsCounter application.
    ReadSymptomDataFromFile
    Simple brute force implementation of reading symptom data from a file.
    WriteSymptomDataToFile
    Simple brute force implementation of writing symptom data to a file.
